{"tid":548594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"心碎！美將中國與流氓政權並列 還在微博上公布","createTime":"2018-02-02T16:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T06:02:09.000Z","uid":35790,"like":96,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1f87d842a721a2cd54634fc64e8e5ad3b16473","tid":548594,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"心碎！美將中國與流氓政權並列 還在微博上公布<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpXnN57T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpXnN57T.jpg&h=bc26faf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國駐中國大使館今（2）日下午1點29分，在中國社群平台「微博」撰文表示，將壯大美國勢力，且將中國與「流氓政權」、「恐怖組織」劃上等號，讓中國網友們跳腳。<br />\n<br />\n「美國駐華大使館」摘錄美國總統川普在1月30日發表的國情咨文演說部分內容，PO上中國社群平台「微博」，大意為美國「面對著各種流氓政權、恐怖主義團伙和中國及俄羅斯等挑戰我國利益、我國經濟和我國價值觀的對手」，必須要使美國勢力更為強大，才能保障美國的國際實力。<br />\n許多中國網友見到此文，均做賊喊捉賊，相繼留言指出「最大的流氓就是美國政府啊」、「一個嫉妒他人進步的國家不配稱之為偉大的國家」、「你找死，要被封（帳）號的」、「最大的流氓政權等著美帝來瓦解」、「我們中國人，管這叫做『落後就要挨打』」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2331153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2331153&d=09cucnzjOCWgK%2B46BQjIg8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=83a67886\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2331153&h=31074dbf\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2331153</a>"},{"pid":"2cc121e6f1726dca7dbc1a5c364c9f0bf23b8096","tid":548594,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T16:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f9d47e17d0da3ace863eaa94fe94557b9076ca","tid":548594,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/